Usage: report_timing_derate [-help] [<object_list>]
                            [-delay_corner <delayCornerName>]
                            [-include_inherited] [ [ > | >> ] ]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>                       # List of objects: cells, nets, or library
                                    # cells (string, optional)
-delay_corner <delayCornerName>     # Specifies delay calculation corner
                                    # (string, optional)
-include_inherited                  # Reports the object names from which the
                                    # derating factor values are inherited
                                    # (bool, optional)
> <filename[.gz]>                   # Redirects output to the specified file
                                    # (redirect_operator, optional)
>> <filename[.gz]>                  # Redirects output to the specified file
                                    # (redirect_operator, optional)